# ⚠️ Common Mistakes to Avoid

* ❌ Don’t show YAML too early
* ❌ Don’t go deep into syntax
* ❌ Don’t assume everyone understands pipelines
* ❌ Don’t focus only on tools

---

# 💡 Pro Tip (Very important)

Use **one real project example** (like PaymentServices)

People understand:

👉 Real > Theoretical

